0px"><b>Proposal</b>:</p><p style=3D"padding-top:0px;padding-bottom:0px;fon=
t-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;,sans-serif;line-height:1.15;margin-to=
p:0px">I propose we introduce a Client-Side Metadata Skip-Layer (Lazy Prefe=
tching) within the Spark Connect protocol. Key pillars include:</p><ol star=
t=3D"1" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Google Sans Text&quot;,sans-serif;line-h=
eight:1.15;margin-top:0px"><li style=3D"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0px"><p=
 style=3D"line-height:1.15;margin-top:0px"><b style=3D"line-height:1.15;mar=
