Hi all,

To enable wide-scale community testing of the upcoming Spark 4.2.0 release,
the Apache Spark community has posted a Spark 4.2.0-preview2 release
<https://dist.apache.org/repos/dist/release/spark/spark-4.2.0-preview2>.
This preview is not a stable release in terms of either API or
functionality,
but it is meant to give the community early access to try the code that wil=
l
become Spark 4.2.0. If you would like to test the release, please download
<https://dist.apache.org/repos/dist/release/spark/spark-4.2.0-preview2> it,
and send feedback using either mailing lists
<https://spark.apache.org/community.html> or JIRA
<https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK/?selectedTab=3Dcom.atlassian.j=
ira.jira-projects-plugin:summary-panel>.
The documentation is available at the link
<https://spark.apache.org/docs/4.2.0-preview2/>.

We=E2=80=99d like to thank our contributors and users for their contributio=
ns and
early feedback to this release. This release would not have been possible
without you.
To download Spark 4.2.0-preview2, head over to the download page:
https://dist.apache.org/repos/dist/release/spark/spark-4.2.0-preview2/

To view the documentation:
https://spark.apache.org/docs/preview/

--00000000000043818c064a58db2f
