Subject: [DISCUSS] SPIP: DSV2 Enhanced Partition Stats Filtering
To: Spark dev list <dev@spark.apache.org>
Content-Type: multipart/alternative; boundary="000000000000771a55064b20bb7c"
From: Szehon Ho <szehon.apache@gmail.com>
Reply-To: <dev@spark.apache.org>

