Content-Type: text/plain; charset="UTF-8"

The Travel Assistance Committee are now accepting applications for
Community Over Code Glasgow, 2026. To be held in Glasgow, Scotland between
the 11th and the 15th October.

The Application deadline is set at the 3rd June - so plenty of time to
apply. If you require a Visa then please do apply early, do not wait until
you know if you are accepted or not. Same for Speakers, you should apply
even though you do not know if you will be accepted, so that your
application is in.

Places are limited for Travel Assistance, so those deemed most in need will
get higher priority.

If you do not need assistance to get to Glasgow, but you know of others who
might be interested, then feel free to spread the word!

Good luck to all those that apply.

