Subject: Proposal for Change Data Capture with Spark
To: dev <dev@spark.apache.org>
Content-Type: multipart/alternative; boundary="000000000000787db5064bdf3d89"
From: Nimrod Ofek <ofek.nimrod@gmail.com>
