   1. time-based: =E2=80=9Cchanges between T1 and T2=E2=80=9D
   2. token-based: =E2=80=9Cchanges between (SCN/LSN)=E2=80=9D (Oracle)
   3. format-version-based: =E2=80=9Cchanges between snapshot/version IDs=
=E2=80=9D
   (Delta/Iceberg/Hudi)

this solution seems to aim for 3 only



